// e la EEPROM ESTERNA 24AA1025
// I2C EEPROM 128K x 8 address: 00000-1FFFF, 
// paginata 64K e paginata 128 byte
//
// --- comandi gestiti ---
// E S <delay min>     log start
// E S 0               log stop / pause
// E R <key>           log clear con chiave key = 12379
